Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: A member of Darth Krayt's One Sith, this Nautolan Sith was part of a strikeforce that attacked Emperor Roan Fel during the execution of Operation: Thunderstroke on the planet Agamar. This Sith fought against Jedi Master Hira, killing her with Force lightning.
